5016.name: Custom Pretendo Error
5016.message: Unable to connect to the server. Please try again later. If the problem persists, please make a note of the error code and visit support.nintendo.com.
5016.long_description: Invalid Service Token. Usually indicates the token is expired.
5016.short_solution: Reboot your console and try again.
5016.long_solution: Try again. If the error code still persists reboot your console.
